high_descs: Turn left, move to the shower, turn left, move to the counter
Take the yellow and green sponge from on the counter
Turn around, move to the center of the bath tub, turn left
Put the yellow and green sponge in the bath tub
Turn around, move to the center of the room, turn left, move to the sink
Take the yellow and green sponge from in the sink
Turn around, move to the center of the room, turn right, move to the center of the bath tub
Put the yellow and green sponge in the bath tub

high_descs: Turn around to face the toilet, then turn right, walk straight, turn left when you reach the tub and walk straight to the cabinet.
Grab the sponge on top of the cabinet.
Turn around to face the bathroom sink then turn left to face the tub.
Place the sponge inside the tub.
Turn around, walk straight toward the toilet, turn left to face the bathroom sink and walk straight to the bathroom sink.
Grab the sponge inside the bathroom sink.
Turn around, walk straight toward the cabinet, turn left to face the tub and walk toward the tub.
Place the sponge in the tub beside the other sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place two sponges in the bathroom tub.

high_descs: turn left and walk on over to the sink ahead, then take another left and walk forwards to the bathroom cabinets on the floor at the end of the room
grab the sponge off of the top of the cabinets
move to the right a bit to face the center of the bathtub
place the sponge in the bathroom to the left of the washcloth
turn right and walk over to the sink on the right at the end of the room
grab the sponge out from the inside of the sink
turn left and walk back over to face the center of the tub
place the sponge down in the tub in between the first sponge you put in there and the dirty washcloth
anns.task_desc: place two sponges inside the bathtub
